### Saphron Open Data: Sample notebook on OCR application with extracted handwriting images

This notebook is part of the nan.ai OCR Open Data. This is a sample of a quick OCR implementation using EasyOCR. With this notebook, we want to show you the process in broad strokes (just access it via S3). You can load the data via S3 or download it and change to a local path.

We are developing our own OCR model. You can check it out [here](https://github.com/Saphron-Asia/nan.ai-ml-ocr)

Join the discussion [here](https://github.com/Saphron-Asia/nan.ai-opendata-ocr/discussions).
